## 🚀 How to Run

1. Clone the repo
2. Open it in Unity (2021.3 LTS or similar)
3. Open the `MainScene` and press Play

## 📁 Folder Structure

- `Scripts/` – All gameplay logic and managers
- `ScriptableObjects/` – Item and level data
- `Prefabs/` – Reusable game objects
- `Scenes/` – MainScene, BackupScene
- `UI/` – Menus and canvas setup

